						<h4>Sophie Pinkham</h4>
												<p>Sophie Pinkham is a professor at Cornell University and a former NEH Public Scholar. Her writing on Russia and Ukraine has appeared in the <em>New York Review of Books</em>, <em>New York Times</em>, <em>Guardian</em>, <em>New Yorker</em>, and <em>Harper’s</em>. She lives in Ithaca, New York.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			
